{"tid":1771424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"準備緊一場聲援法國革命 嘅集會","createTime":"2019-12-06T00:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T01:07:01.000Z","uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9dec0a89516640db698da9ea990771b69af50f","tid":1771424,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"從公交系統到能源，教育，醫療，司法和執法部門，數百萬法國人準備在12月5日星期四發起聯合罷工，反對政府的退休改革計畫，有觀察人士認為社會運轉癱瘓程度將直逼1995年。當年希拉克與朱佩的改革挫敗是否會重現在馬克龍和菲利普身上，各大反改革陣營的立場是堅定的，但（起碼截至目前）政府的改革信心也是堅定的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/政治/20191204-癱瘓全國大罷工在即-數百萬法國人堅決反改革-政府堅決不退讓\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%2F20191204-%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E5%8F%8D%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%80%E8%AE%93&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=72910d9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/政治/20191204-癱瘓全國大罷工在即-數百萬法國人堅決反改革-政府堅決不退讓</a><br />\n<br />\n我地香港人都要幫一幫外國人 大家話啱唔啱？"},{"pid":"fc9f22be4160c734746c056f83577c2d72586e20","tid":1771424,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:53:35.000Z","msg":"光復法國 時代革命！"},{"pid":"cfbca68a33e8e4e92dbc19fe1a1da368233d72ea","tid":1771424,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:55:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce881a98be192243e3ab226bcea1f18c70a34106","tid":1771424,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:58:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a271b346c92468e1a4451a45df7e243bfdcaf09","tid":1771424,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:59:29.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好, 但要幫維吾爾先, 佢地真係水深火熱, 大家敵人又係中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427ae995dddc0832cf729d56cfd27f9f91c443c1","tid":177